# G1 further variables

We are adding 2 variables to the model:

* A1: Transdisciplinary Experience
* E3: Transdisciplinary Aspects (compiled into a single ordinal scaled variable)



```{r echo=FALSE, fig.width=16}

corr_matrix_plt(cbind(g1.modf_civil, e1.df_trans, data$transdisciplinaryExp.rate., e3.modf))



```


---

```{r, fig.width=16}
g1.model.df <- as.data.frame(cbind(g1 = g1.modf_civil,
                    e1 = e1.df_trans,
                    trans.exp = data$transdisciplinaryExp.rate.,
                    trans.asp = e3.modf))
g1.model <- lm(data = g1.model.df, g1 ~ e1 + trans.exp + trans.asp + e1)
tab_model(g1.model)

```

